thread.title_full: SecurCare Self Storage reviewed by Christian

author: Christian
title: Christian
text:
Was a little worried after reading a bad review about person at facility.
Was surprised to be greeted and treated very respectful.
Cynthia Terranova was the person that took the time to explain all to me in great detail and gave me a ride to the unit.
Very pleased with how I was serviced and treated.
Would recommend this place for sure.
